    <section class="faq section" id="faq" aria-label="Frequently asked questions">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center reveal">
          <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Common <span class="text-gradient">Questions</span></h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">Everything you need to know about working with an AI creative agency.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-list reveal" id="faqList">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              What is generative AI and how does X DOT AI use it?
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer" role="region">
              <div class="faq-answer-content">
                Generative AI refers to artificial intelligence systems that can create new content ‚Äî including images,
                videos, music, and text ‚Äî from learned patterns. X DOT AI leverages leading generative AI tools to
                produce ad films, music videos, and branded content at a fraction of the traditional cost and timeline,
                while maintaining creative excellence through human-led direction.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              Who are X DOT AI's training workshops designed for?
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer" role="region">
              <div class="faq-answer-content">
                Our AI training workshops are designed for corporate teams, creative agencies, marketing professionals,
                and educational institutions. We offer customized programs ranging from beginner-level AI literacy to
                advanced prompt engineering and AI content production workflows. Each workshop is tailored to your
                team's specific technology readiness and goals.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              How long does it take to produce an AI-generated ad film?
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer" role="region">
              <div class="faq-answer-content">
                An AI-generated ad film can typically be produced in 5‚Äì10 working days, compared to 4‚Äì8 weeks for
                traditional production. This includes concept development, AI generation, editing, sound design, and
                final delivery. Complex projects with multiple revisions may take longer, but the overall timeline is
                significantly faster than conventional methods.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              What industries does X DOT AI serve?
              <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-answer" role="region">
              <div class="faq-answer-content">
                X DOT AI serves a wide range of industries including technology, entertainment, music, fashion, FMCG,
                education, and healthcare. Our AI-powered approach adapts to any sector that needs creative content or
                AI upskilling ‚Äî from startups looking for cost-effective content to enterprises seeking to transform
                their creative pipelines.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
              Can AI replace human creativity in content production?
